\begin{center}

$\int_{\varepsilon}^{X}\frac{\sin x}{x}\;dx=\left[\frac{1-\cos x}{x}\right]_1^X+\int_{\varepsilon}^{X}\frac{1-\cos x}{x^2}\;dx=\frac{1-\cos X}{X}-\frac{1-\cos \varepsilon}{\varepsilon}+\int_{\varepsilon}^{X}\frac{1-\cos x}{x^2}\;dx$.

\end{center}



